sellerCard.oneLiner: Creating New Stuff is My Passion!
sellerCard.description:
My name is Faizan Ali Naqvi (Ali Mehdi is my nickname). I am a software engineer with 4+ years of experience working as a web developer on fiverr. I love art so I love graphics designing.

I have completed 800+ orders on fiverr and successfully completed countless work through other platforms.

Recently in 2021 I am running my blog at digialps website and I am also running my Youtube channel.

With my blogging experience and my Youtube experience I believe I can help you with SEO of your website.

I love 3d modeling and sculpting although still learning it.

Let's have a chat :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: I'm happy to buy a gig from you! To get started, what do I need?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: You will need a domain and hosting account. If you don't have any then don't worry I'll assist you. I'll also need your company logo(optional) & total number of pages for website. e.g. Home, About Us, Services, Contact Us, Blog. I'll further need content (text, images) for these pages.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide domain or hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, I don't provide domain and hosting. I strongly recommend GreenGeeks for hosting but please contact me before registering your website with them.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you build website on your own server?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I can build website on my server and move it over to yours upon completion free of cost.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide revisions?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I provide unlimited revisions. Your 100% satisfaction is my first priority.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Would I be able to easily manage my website from admin panel? I don't have any knowledge of programming.
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, you will be able to easily add / update / delete / maintain website from admin panel without any programming skills. we will provide username and password of admin panel.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will my website be Mobile Friendly?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yeah definitely your website will be Mobile Responsive :)

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can I see some samples of your work
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yeah for sure you can see my samples of previous work :) just drop me a message in inbox to see my latest work.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide support after completing the job?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yeah I Provide Free support already mention in my packages description :) and if you want additional maintenance support then there will be additional charges.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Important Note: Do you give the licenses to the resources(Themes/Plugins) things) that you use in the process?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No. On the off chance that I will utilize any Premium Theme/Plugin, you may need to buy it in the event that you need lifetime support from the developers, none of my Packages/Gigs incorporate a license for the premium theme/plugin. I just have a developer license to utilize it.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why should I give you a message prior to placing an order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: The best way to follow the path is to get in touch to share website details, share ideas, brainstorm solutions, so I would definitely recommend you to contact me so that we can find a solution to your problems, I can also guide you on which package suits you best for you.

reviews_snippet.comment:
So, I recently had a chance to work with this developer, Faizan. We were working on a project that required a website menu. Given my past experiences, I was trying not to set my hopes too high.

I laid out the project details for Faizan, which included some custom JavaScript, CSS, and a touch of PHP. To my pleasant surprise, he really stepped up. He not only delivered the work promptly but also managed to create a very impressive plugin.

Communicating with Faizan was an easy process. He's well-versed in his field and he managed to deliver quickly.

In conclusion, I think you should definitely consider working with Faizan. His work was commendable and he made the entire process quite smooth.
VERY PROFESSIONAL , ANSWERED ALL MY QUESTIONS IMMEDIATELY AND DELIVERED CODE CHANGE AHEAD OF SCHEDULE . I WOULD NOT HESITATE TO WORK WITH  HIM AGAIN
Ali is really impressive! The works was very systematic and swift! I will be getting him again for future jobs and I highly recommend his services!

Ali did everything we asked him to do for our WordPress website. He was quick to do all revisions and never complained about the number of revisions we requested. Not to mention how quickly he built our site as a whole. Fantastic experience and we would certainly hire him again for our future WordPress needs.
HIGHLY recommend this seller.  He managed to do what other sellers and developers told us could not be done.  His communication was clear and delivery of order fast.
